      <title>29 arrested as law enforcement strikes criminal networks behind illegal streaming</title>
      <link>https://www.europol.europa.eu/media-press/newsroom/news/29-arrested-law-enforcement-strikes-criminal-networks-behind-illegal-streaming</link>
      <description>Criminal networks making millions from illegal access to premium sports broadcasts, film and television channels have been targeted in a major international operation coordinated by Bulgaria with Europol’s support. The seven-month operation resulted in 29 arrests, the dismantling of nine organised crime groups and the removal of over 27 000 illegal streaming URLs.Operation KRATOS 2 brought together law enforcement authorities...</description>
